					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p133081">Re: What kind of 3D calculations were used in SuperFX games?</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=133081#p133081"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon Aug 25, 2014 10:35 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
